  "texts": [
    "Ni et al. [181] jointly optimized the transmitted waveform and receive beamforming to maximize the sensing SINR while satisfying the communication SINR constraint.",
    "Zhao et al. [182] investigated the transceiver design for the ISAC system under the case of both perfect and imperfect channel state information (CSI).",
    "Chen et al. [183] developed a generalized transceiver, and both the radar-centric and communication-centric designs were investigated.",
    "Wen et al. [184] focused on the robust transceiver design for MIMO ISAC networks, where the minimum SINR was maximized.",
    "Lessons learnedThe radar-centric ISAC techniques aim at embedding the communication symbols into radar waveforms without degrading the sensing performance significantly."
